We &apos;re inclined to think that perception is like a window on reality as it is .
The theory of evolution is telling us that this is an incorrect interpretation of our perceptions .
Instead , reality is more like a 3D desktop that &apos;s designed to hide the complexity of the real world and guide adaptive behavior .
